### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5132
@contentType = application/json

### Get All Events (Default Pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events?top=20&skip=0
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### Get Events (Custom Pagination - First 5)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events?top=5&skip=0
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### Get Events (Custom Pagination - Next 5)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events?top=5&skip=5
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### Create New Event (Valid)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Test Event from API",
  "description": "This is a test event created via the API",
  "startDate": "2025-10-24T14:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2025-10-24T15:00:00Z"
}

###

### Create Event (Invalid - Missing Title)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "description": "Missing title",
  "startDate": "2025-10-24T14:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2025-10-24T15:00:00Z"
}

